data.description: Beautiful, well-maintained home in the desirable Richmond Park neighborhood. This meticulously maintained 4 bedroom home features a first floor master suite, and an upstairs bonus room. Flowing hardwood floors. The large living room has a gas fireplace and 10ft + ceilings giving more than enough room to gather. Large gourmet kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances. An oversized deck and a huge fenced in backyard. Refrigerator will convey with an acceptable offer.
